comment.body:
@AdamWr the leftovers seem to only be showing on NSFW related ones.

For example, if you visit `https://scrolller.com/r/porn` and accept the 18+ warning, you will see the leftovers within the grid.

Looking at the source code, there's two types of ad leftovers — one with iframes as mentioned above, and another as images which don't have a targeted class, but they are unique as they are the ones that only contain `target="__blank" rel="noopener nofollow"` `<a>` tags, if that can be targeted to be removed.

